    - next-upgrade: Workflow for upgrading Next.js versions.
    - supabase-postgres-best-practices: Database optimization rules.
    - update-docs: Documentation maintenance workflows.
    - vercel-composition-patterns: React component architecture.
    - vercel-react-best-practices: Performance optimization rules.
    - web-design-guidelines: UI/UX audit standards.
